source: TEXT_GAIUSA108_00722_SEQ_00<tab>Ameexia the sylph would beseech an adventurer's assistance.
target: TEXT_GAIUSA108_00722_SEQ_00<tab>Ameexia aimerait qu'on lui vienne en aide.

source: TEXT_GAIUSA108_00722_SEQ_01<tab>Ameexia is afraid to go out in the forest for fear of being attacked by boars. Search suspicious thickets for the fell swine, and put them down to set her mind at ease.
target: TEXT_GAIUSA108_00722_SEQ_01<tab>Ameexia a été attaqué par des monstres à l'extérieur du Refuge. Examinez les buissons agités et éliminez les <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0D110302 /var> et <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 03F207B70202 /var>.

source: TEXT_GAIUSA108_00722_SEQ_02<tab>Your boar-slaying mission was a success. Report back to Ameexia.
target: TEXT_GAIUSA108_00722_SEQ_02<tab>Vous avez éliminé tous les <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0D110302 /var> et <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 03F207B70202 /var>. Allez raconter vos exploits à Ameexia au Refuge.

source: TEXT_GAIUSA108_00722_SEQ_03<tab>Thanks to your efforts, Ameexia can frolic in the forest to her heart's delight once more.
target: TEXT_GAIUSA108_00722_SEQ_03<tab>Grâce à vous, Ameexia semble rassuré et espère pouvoir tran<var 16 /var>quil<var 16 /var>le<var 16 /var>ment prendre le soleil à l'avenir.

source: TEXT_GAIUSA108_00722_TODO_00<tab>Search the thicket and slay the wild boars.
TEXT_GAIUSA108_00722_TODO_01<tab>Search the thicket and slay the tusked hog.

TEXT_GAIUSA108_00722_AMMEXIA_000_000<tab>Oh, walking one, please listen! This one was frolicking in the forest─as this one likes to do─when nasty tusked ones came huffing and puffing and charging! This one was so frightened!
target:
TEXT_GAIUSA108_00722_AMMEXIA_000_000<tab>Brrr<var 1D /var>! Quand je suis sorti, de terribles sangliers m'ont attaqué<var 1D /var>!
Ils rôdent encore par ici, à la recherche de victimes à encorner<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_GAIUSA108_00722_AMMEXIA_000_001<tab>This one is too scared to go back to the forest. Walking one can make tusked ones go away, yes? This one would dance for joy! Tusked ones hide in bushes. Walking one should be careful!
target:
TEXT_GAIUSA108_00722_AMMEXIA_000_001<tab>J'aimerais qu'on leur donne une leçon de ma part, et vous êtes mon seul espoir<var 1D /var>!
Partez donc à leur recherche dans les hautes herbes, leur territoire.

source: TEXT_GAIUSA108_00722_AMMEXIA_000_020<tab>Walking one has made tusked ones go away? This one can play in the forest again? This one thanks walking one! This one is forever and ever walking one's friend!
target:
TEXT_GAIUSA108_00722_AMMEXIA_000_020<tab>Vous avez maté les méchants sangliers<var 1D /var>?
Chic, je vais pouvoir retourner au soleil me rassasier<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_GAIUSA108_00722_POP_MESSAGE_000<tab>The air is pierced by earsplitting squeals!
